<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_35_line_1576490584475_7576">Gnedıge fraw / Als vns ewr hochwirdıkeit <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_35_r1l6"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Streb<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_35_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab></add> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Darvmb wöllen vvir vnſerſelbs botſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_35_r1l7">cʒü ew ſchıcken / dıe <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>müntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_35_r1l8"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſol / vnd vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_35_line_1576490600825_7593">des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> vvir wıllig vnd <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das cʒü allen <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_35_r1l11"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Gallȷ . ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_35" id="17r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Katherina <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Pomern,
                            <expan>pfalczg<ex>re</ex>fin</expan> bey Reyn und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogin</expan> in Beyrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr hochwirdikeit
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Streb<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan></add>,
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, darumb wöllen wir unserselbs botschaft
                        czü ew schicken, die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>müntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sol; und wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wir willig
                        und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das czü allen
                            <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> galli ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
